        <li>To detect, prevent, and address technical issues.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Data Protection</h3>
    <p>
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of your personal information, username, password, transaction information, and data stored on our site.
